name: Mackenzie Core Plus Canadian Fixed Income ETF
longDescription: The ETF seeks a steady flow of income with an emphasis on capital preservation. The Fund investing primarily in investment grade Canadian government, corporate fixed income and or asset-backed securities, in each case with maturities of more than one year, and may hold up to 30 Percentage of its assets in foreign investments.
